{"tid":1379996,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"探射燈：公園清靜三幾晚 歌舞大媽又開壇","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:46.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c862c207ebed5c95772bbbb1d7a8a81c7a43bebd","tid":1379996,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:00:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%9C%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%BE%E6%99%9A-%E6%AD%8C%E8%88%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%8F%88%E9%96%8B%E5%A3%87-024958577.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%2587%2588%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%25B8%2585%25E9%259D%259C%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E6%2599%259A-%25E6%25AD%258C%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%258F%2588%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A3%2587-024958577.html&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy3jBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=f6073719\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%9C%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%BE%E6%99%9A-%E6%AD%8C%E8%88%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%8F%88%E9%96%8B%E5%A3%87-024958577.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e077IEbLt0H0FQpZOcqaCg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/58046010-b0e2-11e9-b77e-600f9925f3da\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fe077IEbLt0H0FQpZOcqaCg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2F58046010-b0e2-11e9-b77e-600f9925f3da&h=bdfad862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環：不斷有觀眾以利是或現金形式向表演者作出打賞。<br />\n<br />\n大媽歌舞問題滋擾多時，月初屯門公園大型抗議活動後，大媽旋即「歸位」，日前趁康文署人員巡視過後，多名歌女照樣開檔，公然接受打賞。多區歌聲四起，中環海旁短短一百米有四檔開大喇叭表演，聲量超過一百分貝；土瓜灣海心公園涼亭大媽日日開個唱，觀眾在亭內違規吸煙，保安在旁卻視而不見。立法會議員指目前法例存在灰色地帶，促請政府及早檢討堵塞漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n保安巡屯門公園 阿伯不滿<br />\n<br />\n地區組織月初發起抗議屯門公園噪音滋擾行動，事隔不足一個月，大媽依舊歌照唱，錢照收。本報日前往屯門公園巡視，約下午二時，廿多名身掛證件的康文署職員和場地保安在公園內巡視，卻引來圍觀的公園阿伯不滿：「叫人細聲啲可以，冇理由話唔畀人唱歌！」保安員即表示只是勸喻，並解釋停止接受使用自娛區新申請的規定。<br />\n<br />\n眾人約三時離開，現場相對於以往「載歌載舞」場景略為冷清，自娛A、B區未見有人表演，但仍有幾檔大媽隨即「開壇」表演。其中以近西鐵站的一檔最受歡迎，兩名中年歌女輪流獻唱，期間接受觀眾打賞，包括百元鈔票和利是。表演至傍晚六時，場地保安提醒表演時段已完結，其中一名歌女獨自走進工業區一大廈內，而她們在短短三小時內，估計收入已逾千元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d1i6TpzlSPx8Vq0.uCmahg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDIy/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/e37369c0-b0e2-11e9-8dbc-f825d35f6a3d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fd1i6TpzlSPx8Vq0.uCmahg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDIy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2Fe37369c0-b0e2-11e9-8dbc-f825d35f6a3d&h=1988dd5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環：歌藝表演檔配備擴音器，儼如小型舞台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dswewEKo0uAHgpuubghAag--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDQ1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/f403d4a0-b0e2-11e9-bdff-ce90bf99e137\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdswewEKo0uAHgpuubghAag--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDQ1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2Ff403d4a0-b0e2-11e9-bdff-ce90bf99e137&h=6fdc9281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門：大媽趁康文署職員離去旋即開檔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ujex0rwP_rPB_4nUg_UKqw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDI4/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/01bed860-b0e3-11e9-9ebc-0e4e0ecea847\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUjex0rwP_rPB_4nUg_UKqw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDI4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2F01bed860-b0e3-11e9-9ebc-0e4e0ecea847&h=8b122d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n土瓜灣：大涼亭內有六、七名男女輪流唱歌，音量達九十分貝。<br />\n<br />\n中環海濱舞台聲浪100分貝<br />\n<br />\n近年大媽舞台遍布港九新界。平日晚上的中環海濱活動空間，約一百米距離內已有四檔開大擴音器的歌藝表演，咪架、拖板、燈光等設備齊全，部分以海報鋪地，儼如小型舞台，歌女引吭高歌，期間不斷有男士走近遞上利是或現金。記者以分貝機量度，其聲量平均達九十分貝，最高更達一百分貝。其中近八號碼頭的歌舞團甚受歡迎，歌女穿上火紅連身裙，不時與支持者握手，估計每小時收入達五、六百元，翻查資料，該歌舞團曾在旺角西洋菜街行人區演出，在屯門公園亦曾有表演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}